function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_PRIEST) then

	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(ID_PRIEST, SNO_IDLE_ANIM)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(ID_PRIEST, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(ID_PRIEST, false)

	tPortal = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_PRIEST, "Portal")
	for i, idPortal in ipairs(tPortal) do
		Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idPortal, 1)
	end

	idShield = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_PRIEST, "Shield")[1]
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idShield)

end
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.EventSend("BossDefeated")
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
     
    for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
        -- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
        -- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drop occurs
        Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorKilled, "FirstTimeReward_Stronghold_AltarOfRuin", idPlayer)
         
        -- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
        Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Stronghold_AltarOfRuin")
		
    end
Hydra.MusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent", "Music_Kehjistan_AltarOfRuin_Stronghold_Complete")
end
